				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the elementary particle of light.  For other uses, see <a href="Photon_(disambiguation)" title="Photon (disambiguation)">Photon (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
