τ</span></span> * <span class="unicode" style="white-space:nowrap;"><span style="text-decoration:overline;">ν</span><span style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:-0.3em; vertical-align:-0.4em; line-height:1.2em; font-size:85%; text-align:left;"><br />
